channel.title: Ip masking ur ip adress

anyone know any program to mask ur ip address i have use hot spot but i want to change it more frequently and im watching videos on megavideo and it says u can watch only for 74 minutes and then wait 54 to continue re-watching. i am trying to watch a tv series on a website that uses megavideo.
